        <abstract> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Kosmos</hi> [by Alexander von Humboldt] has arrived safely.</p> 
            <p>CD acknowledges his presumption in speculating on variation without having worked out his due share of species, but "for nine years it has been anyhow the greatest amusement to me".</p>
